'''馬克·費格斯'''（{{lang-en|'''Mark Fergus'''}}）和'''霍克·奧斯比'''（{{lang-en|'''Hawk Ostby'''}}）都是編劇，他們最著名的作品是《[[末代浩劫|末代浩劫]]》（被提名[[奧斯卡最佳改編劇本獎|奧斯卡最佳改編劇本獎]]）<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.moviefone.com/2007/02/11/children-of-men-who-really-wrote-the-script/ |title = Children of Men: Who Really Wrote the Script? |date = 2007-02-11 |publisher = Moviefone |language = en |access-date = 2017-04-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160904101918/http://www.moviefone.com/2007/02/11/children-of-men-who-really-wrote-the-script/ |archive-date = 2016-09-04 |dead-url = yes }}</ref>和《[[鐵甲奇俠_(電影)|鐵甲奇俠]]》。他們的其他作品包括由費格斯執導的《{{link-en|預知死劫|First Snow (2006 film)}}》<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/19450-exclusive-first-snow-s-mark-fergus |title = Exclusive: First Snow 's Mark Fergus |author = Edward Douglas |date = 2007-03-21 |publisher = comingsoon.net |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-09 |archive-date = 2019-08-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190820001439/https://www.comingsoon.net/movies/features/19450-exclusive-first-snow-s-mark-fergus |dead-url = no }}</ref>，以及《[[天煞西部反撃戰|天煞西部反撃戰]]》。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.aintitcool.com/node/50030 |title = Nordling Interviews Mark Fergus And Hawk Ostby! COWBOYS & ALIENS! AKIRA! TOMB RAIDER! THE WORLD AFTER! |date = 2011-06-14 |publisher = Aint It Cool News |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-09 |archive-date = 2018-12-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181207110354/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/50030 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

他們是電視劇《[[太空無垠|太空無垠]]》的創作人和執行製作人，劇集於2015年12月在[[Syfy|Syfy]]上首次亮相。<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://deadline.com/2014/04/syfy-fives-10-episode-order-to-space-opera-the-expanse-from-mark-fergus-hawk-ostby-alcon-entertainment-713799/ |title = Syfy Gives 10-Episode Order To Space Opera 'The Expanse' From Mark Fergus & Hawk Ostby, Alcon Entertainment |author = Nellie Andreeva |date = 2014-04-11 |publisher = Deadline |language = en |accessdate = 2017-04-09 |archive-date = 2020-02-22 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200222202400/https://deadline.com/2014/04/syfy-fives-10-episode-order-to-space-opera-the-expanse-from-mark-fergus-hawk-ostby-alcon-entertainment-713799/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>

